      <title>markdown中的公式参考</title>
      <link href="markdown%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5latex%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F/2021/01/18/"/>
      <url>markdown%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5latex%E5%85%AC%E5%BC%8F%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F/2021/01/18/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文引自 <a href="https://www.mathjax.org/#samples">mathjax示例</a></p><h2 id="内联公式与行间公式"><a href="#内联公式与行间公式" class="headerlink" title="内联公式与行间公式"></a>内联公式与行间公式</h2><h3 id="内联公式（行内公式）"><a href="#内联公式（行内公式）" class="headerlink" title="内联公式（行内公式）"></a>内联公式（行内公式）</h3><p>可以方便的放在正文中的公式称为内联公式，如：</p><p>二次方程的一般式为$ax^2 + bx +c = 0$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">二次方程的一般式为<span class="built_in">$</span>ax<span class="built_in">^</span>2 + bx +c = 0<span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="行间公式"><a href="#行间公式" class="headerlink" title="行间公式"></a>行间公式</h3><p>需要单独成行的公式称为行间公式，如：<br>二次方程的解为：<br>$$ x =<br>    {-b \pm \sqrt{b^2-4ac }<br>    \over<br>    2a.}<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span> x= &#123;-b <span class="keyword">\pm</span> <span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123;b<span class="built_in">^</span>2-4ac&#125; <span class="keyword">\over</span> 2a.&#125; <span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="符号的使用"><a href="#符号的使用" class="headerlink" title="$ 符号的使用"></a>$ 符号的使用</h3><p>我们发现$符号被用作了<code>公式</code>的分界符<br>当需要使用$号时只需要用<code>\</code>转义就可以了<br>$ ax^2 + bx +c = 0$</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\$ ax^2 + bx +c &#x3D; 0\$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>那 如过要用 \$符号呢</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">\\\$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>那要是 \\\$ 呢<br>如此类推…</p><h2 id="参考公式"><a href="#参考公式" class="headerlink" title="参考公式"></a>参考公式</h2><h3 id="柯西积分"><a href="#柯西积分" class="headerlink" title="柯西积分"></a>柯西积分</h3><p>$$<br>f(a) =<br>    \frac{1}{2\pi i}<br>    \oint<br>        \frac{f(x)}{z-a}<br>    dz<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span> </span><br><span class="line">f(a) = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;1&#125;&#123;2<span class="keyword">\pi</span> i&#125; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\oint</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;f(x)&#125;&#123;z-a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    dz </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Cosines的两角和公式"><a href="#Cosines的两角和公式" class="headerlink" title="Cosines的两角和公式"></a>Cosines的两角和公式</h3><p>$$<br>\cos(\theta + \varphi) =<br>    cos(\theta)cos(\varphi)<br>    -<br>    sin(\theta)sin(\varphi)<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\cos</span>(<span class="keyword">\theta</span> + <span class="keyword">\varphi</span>) = </span><br><span class="line">    cos(<span class="keyword">\theta</span>)cos(<span class="keyword">\varphi</span>) - </span><br><span class="line">    sin(<span class="keyword">\theta</span>)sin(<span class="keyword">\varphi</span>) </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="高斯散度定理"><a href="#高斯散度定理" class="headerlink" title="高斯散度定理"></a>高斯散度定理</h3><p>$$<br>\int_D ({\nabla\cdot} F)dV =<br>    \int_{\partial D}<br>        F\cdot n<br>    dS<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\int</span><span class="built_in">_</span>D (&#123;<span class="keyword">\nabla</span><span class="keyword">\cdot</span>&#125; F)dV = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\int</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> D&#125; </span><br><span class="line">        F<span class="keyword">\cdot</span> n</span><br><span class="line">    dS </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="向量场的旋度"><a href="#向量场的旋度" class="headerlink" title="向量场的旋度"></a>向量场的旋度</h3><p>$$<br>\vec{\nabla} \times \vec{F} =<br>    \left(<br>        \frac{\partial F_z}{\partial y}<br>        -<br>        \frac{\partial F_y}{\partial z}<br>    \right)<br>    \mathbf{i}<br>    +<br>    \left(<br>        \frac{\partial F_x}{\partial z}<br>        -<br>        \frac{\partial F_z}{\partial x}<br>    \right)<br>    \mathbf{j}<br>    +<br>    \left(<br>        \frac{\partial F_y}{\partial x}<br>        -<br>        \frac{\partial F_x}{\partial y}<br>    \right)<br>    \mathbf{k}<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\vec</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\nabla</span>&#125; <span class="keyword">\times</span> <span class="keyword">\vec</span>&#123;F&#125; = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\left</span>( </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> F<span class="built_in">_</span>z&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> y&#125; - </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> F<span class="built_in">_</span>y&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> z&#125; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\right</span>) </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\mathbf</span>&#123;i&#125; + </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\left</span>( </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> F<span class="built_in">_</span>x&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> z&#125; - </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> F<span class="built_in">_</span>z&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> x&#125; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\right</span>) </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\mathbf</span>&#123;j&#125; + </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\left</span>( </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> F<span class="built_in">_</span>y&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> x&#125; - </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> F<span class="built_in">_</span>x&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> y&#125; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\right</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\mathbf</span>&#123;k&#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="标准差"><a href="#标准差" class="headerlink" title="标准差"></a>标准差</h3><p>$$<br>\sigma =<br>    \sqrt{<br>        \frac{1}{N}<br>        \sum_{i=1}^N<br>            (x_i - \mu)^2<br>     }<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sigma</span> = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;1&#125;&#123;N&#125; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\sum</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;i=1&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>N </span><br><span class="line">            (x<span class="built_in">_</span>i - <span class="keyword">\mu</span>)<span class="built_in">^</span>2</span><br><span class="line">     &#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="克里斯托费尔符号（Christoffel-Symbols-的定义"><a href="#克里斯托费尔符号（Christoffel-Symbols-的定义" class="headerlink" title="克里斯托费尔符号（Christoffel Symbols)的定义"></a>克里斯托费尔符号（Christoffel Symbols)的定义</h3><p>$$<br>(\nabla_X Y)^k =<br>    X^i (\nabla_i Y)^k =<br>    X^i \left(<br>            \frac{\partial Y^k}{\partial x^i} +<br>            \Gamma_{im}^k Y^m<br>        \right)<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">\nabla</span><span class="built_in">_</span>X Y)<span class="built_in">^</span>k = </span><br><span class="line">    X<span class="built_in">^</span>i (<span class="keyword">\nabla</span><span class="built_in">_</span>i Y)<span class="built_in">^</span>k =</span><br><span class="line">    X<span class="built_in">^</span>i <span class="keyword">\left</span>(</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> Y<span class="built_in">^</span>k&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\partial</span> x<span class="built_in">^</span>i&#125; + </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">\Gamma</span><span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;im&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>k Y<span class="built_in">^</span>m </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">\right</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="矩阵"><a href="#矩阵" class="headerlink" title="矩阵"></a>矩阵</h3><p>$$<br>A = \begin{bmatrix}<br>        {a_{11}} &amp; {a_{12}} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {a_{1n}} \<br>        {a_{21}} &amp; {a_{22}} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {a_{2n}} \<br>        {\vdots} &amp; {\vdots} &amp; {\ddots} &amp; {\vdots} \<br>        {a_{11}} &amp; {a_{12}} &amp; {\cdots} &amp; {a_{1n}} \<br>    \end{bmatrix}<br>\tag{1.1}<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line">A = </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;bmatrix&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;11&#125;&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;12&#125;&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\cdots</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;1n&#125;&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;21&#125;&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;22&#125;&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\cdots</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;2n&#125;&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;<span class="keyword">\vdots</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\vdots</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\ddots</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\vdots</span>&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;11&#125;&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;12&#125;&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;<span class="keyword">\cdots</span>&#125; <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> &#123;a<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;1n&#125;&#125;<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;bmatrix&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\tag</span>&#123;1.1&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="mhchem-化学公式"><a href="#mhchem-化学公式" class="headerlink" title="mhchem 化学公式"></a>mhchem 化学公式</h2><p>$\ce{H2 + \frac{1}{2}O2 -&gt;[点燃] \frac{1}{2}H2O }$</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\ce</span>&#123;H2 + <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;1&#125;&#123;2&#125;O2 -&gt;[点燃] <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;1&#125;&#123;2&#125;H2O &#125;<span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="语法元素"><a href="#语法元素" class="headerlink" title="语法元素"></a>语法元素</h2><p>这一节参考至<a href>一份(不太)简短的Latex2e介绍</a></p><h3 id="需要转义的符号"><a href="#需要转义的符号" class="headerlink" title="需要转义的符号"></a>需要转义的符号</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="right">{</th><th align="left"><code>\&#123;</code></th><th align="right">}</th><th align="left"><code>\&#125;</code></th><th align="right">$</th><th align="left"><code>\$</code></th><th align="right">%</th><th align="left"><code>\%</code></th></tr></thead></table><h3 id="希腊字母"><a href="#希腊字母" class="headerlink" title="希腊字母"></a>希腊字母</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="right">$\alpha$</th><th align="left"><code>\alpha</code></th><th align="right">$\theta$</th><th align="left"><code>\theta</code></th><th align="right">$o$</th><th align="left"><code>o</code></th><th align="right">$\upsilon$</th><th align="left"><code>\upsilon</code></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="right">$\beta$</td><td align="left"><code>\beta</code></td><td align="right">$\vartheta$</td><td align="left"><code>\vartheta</code></td><td align="right">$\pi$</td><td align="left"><code>\pi</code></td><td align="right">$\phi$</td><td align="left"><code>\phi</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\gamma$</td><td align="left"><code>\gamma</code></td><td align="right">$\iota$</td><td align="left"><code>\iota</code></td><td align="right">$\varpi$</td><td align="left"><code>\varpi</code></td><td align="right">$\varphi$</td><td align="left"><code>\varphi</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\delta$</td><td align="left"><code>\delta</code></td><td align="right">$\kappa$</td><td align="left"><code>\kappa</code></td><td align="right">$\rho$</td><td align="left"><code>\rho</code></td><td align="right">$\chi$</td><td align="left"><code>\chi</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\epsilon$</td><td align="left"><code>\epsilon</code></td><td align="right">$\lambda$</td><td align="left"><code>\lambda</code></td><td align="right">$\varrho$</td><td align="left"><code>\varrho</code></td><td align="right">$\psi$</td><td align="left"><code>\psi</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\varepsilon$</td><td align="left"><code>\varepsilon</code></td><td align="right">$\mu$</td><td align="left"><code>\mu</code></td><td align="right">$\sigma$</td><td align="left"><code>\sigma</code></td><td align="right">$\omega$</td><td align="left"><code>\omega</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\zeta$</td><td align="left"><code>\zeta</code></td><td align="right">$\nu$</td><td align="left"><code>\nu</code></td><td align="right">$\varsigma$</td><td align="left"><code>\varsigma</code></td><td align="right"></td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\eta$</td><td align="left"><code>\eta</code></td><td align="right">$\xi$</td><td align="left"><code>\xi</code></td><td align="right">$\tau$</td><td align="left"><code>\tau</code></td><td align="right"></td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\Gamma$</td><td align="left"><code>\Gamma</code></td><td align="right">$\Lambda$</td><td align="left"><code>\Lambda</code></td><td align="right">$\Sigma$</td><td align="left"><code>\Sigma</code></td><td align="right">$\Psi$</td><td align="left"><code>\Psi</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\Delta$</td><td align="left"><code>\Delta</code></td><td align="right">$\Xi$</td><td align="left"><code>\Xi</code></td><td align="right">$\Upsilon$</td><td align="left"><code>\Upsilon</code></td><td align="right">$\Omega$</td><td align="left"><code>\Omega</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\Theta$</td><td align="left"><code>\Theta</code></td><td align="right">$\Pi$</td><td align="left"><code>\Pi</code></td><td align="right">$\Phi$</td><td align="left"><code>\Phi</code></td><td align="right"></td><td align="left"></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\varGamma$</td><td align="left"><code>\varGamma</code></td><td align="right">$\varLambda$</td><td align="left"><code>\varLambda</code></td><td align="right">$\varSigma$</td><td align="left"><code>\varSigma</code></td><td align="right">$\varPsi$</td><td align="left"><code>\varPsi</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\varDelta$</td><td align="left"><code>\varDelta</code></td><td align="right">$\varXi$</td><td align="left"><code>\varXi</code></td><td align="right">$\varUpsilon$</td><td align="left"><code>\varUpsilon</code></td><td align="right">$\varOmega$</td><td align="left"><code>\varOmega</code></td></tr><tr><td align="right">$\varTheta$</td><td align="left"><code>\varTheta</code></td><td align="right">$\varPi$</td><td align="left"><code>\varPi</code></td><td align="right">$\varPhi$</td><td align="left"><code>\varPhi</code></td><td align="right"></td><td align="left"></td></tr></tbody></table><p>累了 不想打字了 有空在续吧$\cdots$</p><!-- TODO: 修饰符号 --><!-- TODO：运算符号 --><script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.2.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.2.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content>
      
      
